Description: ****************************************
        taileff: tail -f for humans
        ****************************************
        
        .. image:: taileff_showcase.gif
        
        taileff makes it easier to read the output of tail -f, using features such as:
        
        * syntax highlighting
        * line numbering
        * separating lines
        * grouping separators
        * indentation (only for SQL atm)
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            $ pip install taileff
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        .. code-block:: bash
        
            $ tailf <file> [-s -i -n -l <language> -g <seconds>]
            $ tailf --help
        
        
        Licence
        -------
        
        BSD
        
